    "Our implementation for inference using the optimized adversarial set is showcased in Algorithm 3.",
    "We run our experiments on an Intel Xeon Gold 6226R CPU with an NVIDIA RTX A6000 GPU.",
    "The environment is configured with Python 3.10.8.",
    "For the settings of each process in the universal jailbreak attack, we set the time limit to 150,000 seconds.",
    "In the defense setup, we also set the same time limit for optimizing defense multi-prompts in DUMP."
